Name: Log Service Message Registry
Description: This registry defines the messages for log service related events

DiagnosticDataCollected.Description: Indicates that diagnostic data has been collected due to a client invoking the `CollectDiagnosticData` action.
DiagnosticDataCollected.LongDescription: This message shall be used to indicate that diagnostic data has been collected due to a client invoking the `CollectDiagnosticData` action.
ArgLongDescriptions: The value of this argument shall be a string containing the `DiagnosticDataType` parameter provided by the client when the `CollectDiagnosticData` action was invoked.
